import{_ as i,c as t,o,a8 as a}from"./chunks/framework.n3V8RT1I.js";const h=JSON.parse('{"title":"四级","description":"","frontmatter":{},"headers":[],"relativePath":"english/四级/index.md","filePath":"english/四级/index.md","lastUpdated":1765935507000}'),s={name:"english/四级/index.md"};function n(r,e,l,u,c,p){return o(),t("div",null,e[0]||(e[0]=[a('<h1 id="四级" tabindex="-1">四级 <a class="header-anchor" href="#四级" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;四级&quot;">​</a></h1><h2 id="作文" tabindex="-1">作文 <a class="header-anchor" href="#作文" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;作文&quot;">​</a></h2><p>模版：</p><p>第一段：引出话题 (The Opening) Nowadays, there is a growing discussion about [文章主题词]. It has sparked heated debate among the public. [此处可选填: As is vividly shown in the picture...] It is generally believed that [主题词] plays a vital role in our daily lives / personal growth.To elaborate on my point, we should consider it from the following perspectives.</p><p>中文释义： 如今，关于[主题词]的讨论越来越多。它已成为公众的热门话题。（如图所示……）。人们普遍认为[主题词]在我们的日常生活/个人成长中扮演着至关重要的角色。为了更好地论证，我们应该从不同角度来分析。</p><p>第二段：论证分析 (The Body) To begin with, [论点1]. This means that if we [做某事], we can [得到什么好处].</p><p>Moreover, [论点2]. There is no denying that [主题词] enables us to [做某事], which is beneficial to our future career.</p><p>第三段：总结建议 (The Conclusion) In conclusion, [主题词] is indispensable to everyone. It is high time that we took effective measures to [重视它/培养它/解决它]. Only in this way can we have a bright future.</p><p>中文释义： 总之，[主题词]对每个人都是不可或缺的。是时候采取有效措施来……了。只有这样，我们要才能拥有美好的未来。</p><p>练习案例1：Self-discipline</p><p>The Importance of Self-discipline</p><p>[Introduction] Nowadays, the importance of self-discipline has sparked heated debate among the public. It is generally believed that self-discipline plays a vital role in our daily lives.</p><p>[Analysis] To begin with, self-discipline enables us to cultivate healthy habits, which ensures we make continuous progress in our work and academic study. Moreover, it can prevent us from laziness and anxiety, making our lives more fulfilling and meaningful.</p><p>[Conclusion] In conclusion, self-discipline is the key to success. Without it, we can accomplish nothing. As college students, we should cultivate this habit consciously. We are advised to set strict plans for both our studies and daily lives, and more importantly, stick to them faithfully.</p><h2 id="_2025" tabindex="-1">2025 <a class="header-anchor" href="#_2025" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;2025&quot;">​</a></h2><h3 id="第一套" tabindex="-1">第一套 <a class="header-anchor" href="#第一套" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;第一套&quot;">​</a></h3><p>suppose your university is organizing a forum on the development of students cross-cultural communication abilities.</p><p>Nowadays, there is a growing discussion about the development of students cross-cultural communication abilities. It has sparked heated debate among the university students forum. It is generally believed that the cross-cultural communication abilities plays a vital role in our personal growth. To elaborate on my point, we should consider it from the following perspectives.</p><p>To begin with, the cross-cultural communication abilities enables us to understand the different cultures and customs of different countries. This helps us to build a more open and inclusive mindset, and to respect the diversity of cultures. Moreover, it allows us to communicate with people from different countries, which is no denying that it is beneficial to our future career.</p><p>In conclusion, the cross-cultural communication abilities is indispensable to everyone. It is high time that we took effective measures to cultivate this ability.</p><h3 id="第二套" tabindex="-1">第二套 <a class="header-anchor" href="#第二套" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;第二套&quot;">​</a></h3><p>suppose your university is conducting a survey to collect students&#39; opinions on the appropriate use of AI technology in assisting learning. You are now to write an essay to express your view.</p><p>Nowadays, there is a growing discussion about the appropriate use of AI technology in assisting learning. It has sparked heated debate among college students. It is generally believed that AI technology plays a vital role in our daily study. To elaborate on my point, we should consider it from the following perspectives.</p><p>To begin with, AI technology helps us improve our learning efficiency and develop practical abilities. This means that if we use AI tools to review difficult concepts and practice exercises, we can make steady progress in our studies.</p><p>Moreover, AI-assisted learning plays an important role in our future career. There is no denying that AI enables us to acquire new skills more quickly and adapt to the changing job market, which is beneficial to our future development.</p><p>In conclusion, the appropriate use of AI technology is indispensable to modern education. It is high time that we took effective measures to use AI responsibly and wisely. Only in this way can we have a bright future.</p><h2 id="四级作文万能模版整理" tabindex="-1">四级作文万能模版整理 <a class="header-anchor" href="#四级作文万能模版整理" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;四级作文万能模版整理&quot;">​</a></h2><h3 id="一、三段通用模版" tabindex="-1">一、三段通用模版 <a class="header-anchor" href="#一、三段通用模版" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;一、三段通用模版&quot;">​</a></h3><p>第一段（引出话题）：</p><p>Nowadays, there is a growing discussion about [topic].<br> It has sparked heated debate among the public / college students.<br> It is generally believed that [topic] plays a vital role in our daily lives / personal growth.<br> To elaborate on my point, we should consider it from the following perspectives.</p><p>第二段（论证分析）总结构：</p><p>To begin with, [argument 1]. is characterized by its wide variety of xxx. So that it is not only help you to accumulate adequate knowledge of xxx around the world, bug also arouse your passion for the xxx and bring you an opportunity to make new friends.</p><p>Moreover, [argument 2].<br> There is no denying that [topic] enables us to [具体能力/结果], which is beneficial to our future study / career / personal development.</p><p>第三段（总结建议）：</p><p>In conclusion, [topic] is indispensable to everyone.<br> It is high time that we took effective measures to cultivate xxx habit.</p><h3 id="二、第二段常用论点方向与示例" tabindex="-1">二、第二段常用论点方向与示例 <a class="header-anchor" href="#二、第二段常用论点方向与示例" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;二、第二段常用论点方向与示例&quot;">​</a></h3><p>（一）学习与能力提升角度</p><p>通用句型：<br> [topic] helps us improve our learning efficiency and develop practical abilities.<br> This means that if we [form the habit of + 行为], we can make steady progress in our studies.</p><p>Self-discipline 示例：<br> Self-discipline helps us form good study habits and stay focused on our goals.<br> If we strictly follow our study plans every day, we can gradually improve our grades.</p><p>（二）身心健康角度</p><p>通用句型：<br> [topic] contributes greatly to our physical and mental health.<br> When we [具体行为], we are less likely to suffer from stress and anxiety, and can enjoy a healthier life.</p><p>Self-discipline 示例：<br> Self-discipline helps us control our screen time and keep a regular schedule.<br> If we go to bed early and exercise regularly, we will feel more energetic and confident.</p><p>（三）人际关系与沟通能力角度</p><p>通用句型：<br> [topic] enables us to build better relationships with others.<br> By learning to [具体行为], we can communicate more effectively and win others&#39; respect and trust.</p><p>Cross-cultural communication 示例：<br> Cross-cultural communication abilities enable us to understand different cultures and customs.<br> This helps us develop an open and inclusive attitude towards people from different backgrounds.</p><p>（四）未来就业与职业发展角度</p><p>通用句型：<br> [topic] plays an important role in our future career.<br> There is no denying that employers prefer those who have [品质/能力], which can greatly increase our competitiveness in the job market.</p><p>Cross-cultural communication 示例：<br> Cross-cultural communication abilities allow us to work effectively in international teams,<br> which is greatly beneficial to our future development in the job market.</p><p>（五）社会意义与长远影响角度</p><p>通用句型：<br> [topic] is also of great importance to society as a whole.<br> When more people realize the importance of [topic], our society will become more harmonious and progressive.</p><p>Environmental protection 示例：<br> Environmental awareness is of great importance to the sustainable development of our society.<br> If everyone saves energy and reduces waste in daily life, we can protect our planet for future generations.</p><p>Nowadays, there is a growing discussion about the appropriate use of AI technology in assisting learning. It has sparked heated debate among college students. It is generally believed that AI plays a vital role in our daily study. To elaborate on my point, we should consider it from the following perspectives.</p><p>To begin with, AI-assisted learning is characterized by its wide variety of educational tools. So that it not only helps you to accumulate adequate knowledge of different subjects around the world, but also arouses your passion for learning and brings you an opportunity to make new friends in online study groups.</p><p>Moreover, AI technology can provide personalized learning suggestions. There is no denying that AI enables us to improve our study efficiency and accuracy, which is beneficial to our future academic and career development.</p><p>In conclusion, AI technology is indispensable to modern education. It is high time that we took effective measures to use AI responsibly, such as setting clear guidelines and avoiding over-reliance on it.</p><h2 id="翻译" tabindex="-1">翻译 <a class="header-anchor" href="#翻译" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;翻译&quot;">​</a></h2><p>In recent years, northeast china is vigorously developing the ice and snow resources. For example, harbin utilized the adequate ice and snow resources to build the &quot;Big Ice and Snow World&quot; which is characterized by ist localized features</p>',57)]))}const f=i(s,[["render",n]]);export{h as __pageData,f as default};
